ATA[festizio]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wholesome</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1Zstttm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QWpGXXb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1Zstttm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GorgeousGeorgieous]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When did not aspiring to have kids become so taboo?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tO1U3qz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/waWlngR.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>TLDR: Stop telling people they are immature or they're crazy or anything else insulting for choosing not to have kids.

I'm almost 30. From the moment I got married at 24, my mother has been asking for grand babies. I never ever wanted kids, I knew this since I was 15. 

The world is chaotic, it's not sustainable, there is overpopulation, and living is fucking hard. Not to mention the medical risk it is for anyone to give birth, or the cost it would be to have a surrogate, or literally having a child out of moral obligation when you're not mentally prepared and how unfair that is to everyone in any situation. 

I'm not shittin on people who make it work and literally find their joy and purpose when they have a child, because I know being afraid and not wanting a baby can change when they're born. I know that happens. I have a friend who got pregnant early and I love her son, I'm so proud of her, there are literal super people out there doing this against all odds.

It's just, if I chose not to have a child, how does that make me immature? If I die, my money, whatever little there is left because I plan on fucking living, won't get passed down, we won't leave a legacy, we won't continue our family bloodline etc etc. Why is that all important? I just wanna fucking live man, travel and for once not feel like I'm in a motherfuckin box of a life chained to money and obligations simply because society said that's 'normal'.

Anyways. It was bothering me cuz posts like that were increasing lately, then I kept seeing El*n having his too many children and talking about repopulation because of the decline in births. But why on this dying overpopulated planet is that a fucking concern?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tO1U3qz</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SaffronGin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Xvo3k49</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0t1LX8f.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Xvo3k49</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Umgurbanned]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Still Going Strong!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Ia6sNth</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IpxxzFV.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ay612ar.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZCIKt7R.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0hQCUBk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/26bhwTB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x4yJ362.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2fObNYh.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vwFZPYH.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vhejNee.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x3NL0xy.png" style="max-width